order_management_demo (Dart / Jaspr port)

This project is a rewrite of the Restaurant Order Management demo, ported from
TypeScript (Deno Fresh) to Dart (Jaspr + SQLite).

Original work
  Project:  order-management-demo
  Authors:  Fraktalio D.O.O. (https://github.com/fraktalio)
